OL,6,FJersey's only child contact centre is
OL,7,Fat risk of closure if extra funding is
OL,8,Fnot found urgently.
OL,10,FThe site is run by the local charity
OL,11,FCentrepoint and provides a safe space
OL,12,Ffor children and their parents who do
OL,13,Fnot have custody.
OL,15,FIn 2023, the Government gave them
OL,16,F#81,000 of funding to open and operate
OL,17,Fthe centre for a year.
OL,19,FIt then extended the contract until
OL,20,Flast December but this has now expired
OL,21,Fand the money has run out.
