OL,3,CJersey's only child contact centre at
OL,4,Crisk of closure
OL,6,FJane Moy, Chief Executive Officer of
OL,7,FCentrepoint, says the charity does not
OL,8,Fwant to close the centre but may have
OL,9,Fno choice if more money is not
OL,10,Fprovided.
OL,12,FShe explains: "To suddenly have
OL,13,Fanother financial burden such as the
OL,14,Fcontact centre which we were asked to
OL,15,Fset up, I was very angry when I heard
OL,16,Fthey were pulling funding but more
OL,17,Fthan that, I was very disappointed."
