OL,3,CJersey's only child contact centre at
OL,4,Crisk of closure
OL,6,FThe service was previously provided by
OL,7,FMilli's Separated Family Centre but
OL,8,Fthe charity closed in 2023 due to new
OL,9,Fregulations.
OL,11,FCentrepoint is currently helping 17
OL,12,Fdifferent families and had five new
OL,13,Freferrals last week.
OL,15,FChild Contact Centre Manager Tyler
OL,16,FGosselin says the work they do is
OL,17,Fvital.
