OL,4,Crisk of closure
OL,6,FHe adds: "Some of the children only
OL,7,Fget to see their visiting parent once
OL,8,Fa week using our service. It's really
OL,9,Fnice to see that big smile on the
OL,10,Fchild's and parent's face.
OL,12,F"Parents are aware of our financial
OL,13,Fsituation. It's very difficult for
OL,14,Fthem because this is where a lot have
OL,15,Fcontact and there's nowhere else. So
OL,16,Fthey were quite sad and probably feel
OL,17,Fquite let down."
