OL,6,FIn response to ITV News's request,
OL,7,FDeputy Malcolm Ferey, Jersey's
OL,8,FAssistant Minister for Children and
OL,9,FFamilies, says: "The Government is
OL,10,Fhelping Centrepoint to seek
OL,11,Fappropriate funding for this year from
OL,12,Falternative sources and, moving
OL,13,Fforward, other funding solutions will
OL,14,Fneed to be found."
